responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "78C592EF45203188AC4B2E88A4221BD4", "Far be it from me to stop you. I\'m hardly your boss. If you head that way though, would you be so kind as to bring back any intel you find? Entrances and guard towers are of import. Also, the strength of their resistance, perhaps?")
